title: where the god of love hangs out
description:
where the god of love hangs out by Amy Bloom


a collection of short stories.



a couple of middle aged academics have a cladenstine affair.

a widow is having sex with her grieving stepson.

a young girl is in bereavement.

a young woman shares the secrets of her past with her old father in law who thinks about leaving his loving wife.



to love for better or for worse as they say, either way love will mess you up.
